<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(11, 71, 157);" align="center"><b>Fabulous Feedback!</b></p>
<div style="text-align: center;" align="center"><b><em>Here's What We've Heard About Our Sitters</em><br /></b></div>
<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(11, 71, 157);" align="center"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp;</b></p>
<p style="font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><b></b></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>"I just wanted to drop you a note and let you know how happy we were to have Kalyn watch our children.&nbsp; We were able to go out and not worry about calling home every hour to check on everyone.&nbsp; My boys loved her and look forward to her visiting again.&nbsp; Thank you so much for accommodating us on so short a notice.&nbsp; We will definitely recommend Rocket City Sitters to everyone we know with children and will call to have Kalyn watch our boys again."</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><em> - Barbara F. of Madison, mother of two</em></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>"Morgan was here today to watch my 3 youngest and I'm glowing with how wonderful she is. Thank you so much for this service and for Morgan. I couldn't have asked for a better experience."</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><em> - Bianca S. of Huntsville, mother of six</em></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;" align="center"><span>Find out what other parents are saying on our <a style="color: rgb(3, 71, 157); text-decoration: underline;" track="on" shape="rect" href="http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?e=0012TOuDM26yPAewYEOMFWPcZsbV_8xl63R9nrxc4HHPzf7RRdI-M0V2Dl4dEoAypOt_nToGyJ0XzIfbisEBpfRqCx2V7GA1oxdhYW2cUGNxdga8UAlFaoUz5ewgSjvBN9GGBV_szF29aqTvwXR0gXyioBdcpV8R-29FBr4nilvW-ywbkb_30SOJYPnCErhacI3r553FS78TpDPb2uS7SfOegP_z5MyK2se841xDEEsAVWIlpXcaSOXj1qyIvxKQ8Jhg9iUoBBZL-r3AynrYYYCxfPkBSlzc8PeBPmscM2NGF0=" linktype="1" target="_blank">Parents Page</a>.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;" align="center"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<div style="text-align: center;" align="center"><span>Do you love your sitter? <a style="color: rgb(3, 71, 157); text-decoration: underline;" href="mailto:info@rocketcitysitters.com" shape="rect" linktype="2" target="_blank">Email us</a> and let us know!<br /><br /></span></div>
<p style="font-size: 8pt; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;" align="center"><a style="color: rgb(12, 71, 157); text-decoration: underline; font-family: Trebuchet MS,Geneva;" href="#Top" shape="rect">Back to Top</a>&nbsp;</p>
