<div style="text-align: left;" align="left">
<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;" align="center"><span style="color:#0c479d;font-family:Trebuchet MS,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:18pt;"><b> Meet Meagan!&nbsp;</b></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Trebuchet MS,Geneva; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;" align="left"><span style="font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>This issue's featured sitter is Meagan Hunt, who has been with Rocket City Sitters since October of 2010. Meagan decided to start working with Rocket City Sitters because she's a full time law student and her schedule doesn't allow her to have a typical job. Meagan says, "I have always enjoyed kids and babysitting and once I found out about RCS I knew it was perfect for me."</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp; </span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>In addition to being a law student, Meagan is also an extern with the Madison County DA and is an independent consultant with Scentsy, Inc. In May, Meagan will graduate from Cumberland Law School (but don't worry, she plans to continue being a sitter post-graduation!) and in September she's looking forward to marrying her boyfriend of eight years.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>Meagan is requested often because families love her sweet nature and her way with kids.</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span><em>"We loved Meagan! She was great with our girls; both of them just loved her. We're very happy and will definitely be using RCS again very soon! Thank you so much for providing such a great service." - Lindsay B. of Huntsville, mother of two</em></span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
<span>To schedule Meagan, or another one of our great sitters, call us at 256-272-1727.</span><br /></div>
